# Rules
- use pnpm

# Tree
- `apps/api` : API backend (NestJS)
- `apps/web-spa` : frontend SPA (React/Vite)
- `apps/web-ssr` : frontend SSR
- `packages/` : Shared packages
- `packages/ui` : UI library package (using shadcn and Tailwind)
- `packages/openapi-generator` : generated client library, containing types, schemas, sdks

# Rules

- Always switch to the correct node version when running commands. Use `fnm use` to switch to the correct node version. Try `nvm use` if fnm is not available.